channel.title: Jupiter - Hern [Electronic]
channel.description:
New single from my upcoming LP, "Empyreal." Going back to the space them I started this account with, but with a musical style more akin to my work with Vokon and the Intrepid EP. This will probably be the last single released from this project before I put the whole thing out there.
Link is here: https://soundcloud.com/hernmusicofficial/jupiter
Hope you guys enjoy, constructive criticism is welcome as always.
